# Fortune.com Commercial Services Related to Business Development

## Business Development
Fortune provides partners across the globe with access to relevant and timely content for every platform, partnering with media outlets and corporations across 27 countries. From news feeds and video to reprints, data and more, Fortune offers premium content and develops innovative relationships through its Business Development Team.

## Related Distribution Services
- **Traditional Syndication** – Distribution of Fortune content through traditional news syndication channels.
- **Google News** – Fortune content appears on Google News platforms.
- **Yahoo News** – Fortune content appears on Yahoo News platforms.
- **Bloomberg** – Fortune content is syndicated to Bloomberg.
- **Facebook** – Fortune content shared on Facebook.
- **MSN** – Fortune content distributed via MSN.
- **YouTube** – Fortune video content on YouTube.
